| 8 | 1.0 | 8.0x | 8.5 | 90% | 35% |
| 12 | 1.2 | 6.7x | 8.1 | 92% | 40% |

## 🔧 Troubleshooting

### Device Issues

```python
from nanoquant import get_device_info

# Check your device setup
info = get_device_info()
print(f"Platform: {info['platform']}")
print(f"Optimal device: {info['optimal_device']}")
print(f"CUDA available: {info['cuda_available']}")
print(f"MPS available: {info['mps_available']}")
```

### Memory Optimization

```python
config = NanoQuantConfig(
    model_name="meta-llama/Llama-2-70b-hf",
    rank=4,  # Lower rank = less memory
    calib_samples=32,  # Fewer samples
    batch_size=1,  # Smaller batches
    device="cuda",
)
```

